hadiths[26]{hadithnumber,text}:
1198,"aap aik raat Ummul-Momenin Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan soey. Ummul-Momenin Memuna (Raziallahu anha) aap ki khala thin. aap ne bayan kya ke main bistar ke arz (chaudaan) mein let gaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ki biwi iske tool (lambaan) mein letey. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey yahan tak ke aadhi raat hui ya us se thodi der pahley ya baad . to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bedaar ho kar baith gaey aur chehrey se neend ke khumaar ko apne donon hathon se door karne lagey. phir sura aale-Imraan ke aakhir ki das aayatein padhein iske baad pani ki aik mashk ke paas gaey jo latak rahi thi, us se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne achi tarah wuzu kya, phir khadey ho kar Namaz shuru ki. Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main bhi utha aur jis tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya tha maine bhi kya aur phir ja kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke pahlu mein khada ho gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna daahinaa hath mere sar par rakha aur mere daahiney kaan ko pakad kar usey apne hath se modney lagey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 rakaat Namaz padhi, phir 2 rakaat padhi, phir 2 rakaat padhi, phir 2 rakaat padhi, phir 2 rakaat padhi, phir 2 rakaat padhi. iske baad (eik rakaat ( witr padha aur let gaey. jab muazzan aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dobara uthey aur 2 halki rakatein padh kar bahar Namaz ( fajr (ke liye tashrif ley gaey."
1199,(pahley ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhtey hotey aur ham salam kartey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iska jawab detey they. jab ham Najashi ke yahan se wapas huey to ham ne (pahley ki tarah Namaz hi mein) salam kya. lekin us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab nahi diya balke Namaz se farigh ho kar farmaya ke Namaz mein aadmi ko fursat kahan .
1200,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein Namaz padhney mein baatein kar liya kartey they. koi bhi apne qareeb ke namazi se apni zarurat bayan kar detaa. phir aayat (حافظوا على الصلوات‏..) utri aur hamein (namaz mein) khamosh rehney ka hukm hua.
1201,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) banu-Amr-bin-Auf ( Quba (ke logon mein suleh karwaaney tashrif laaey, aur jab Namaz ka waqt ho gaya to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to ab tak nahi tashrif laey isliye ab aap Namaz padhaaiye. unhon-ne farmaya achchha agar tumhari khahish hai to main padha deta hun. khair Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne takbeer kahi Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aagey badhey aur Namaz shuru ki. itney main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif ley aaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safon se guzartey huey pehli saf tak pahunch gaey. logon ne hath par hath maarna shuru kya. (Sahal ne) kaha ke jantey ho ( تصفيح‏ ( kya hai yani taaliyaan bajaanaa aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz mein kisi taraf bhi dhyaan nahi kya kartey they, lekin jab logon ne zyada taaliyaan bajaaiin to aap mutwajjeh huey. kya dekhtey hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) saf mein maujood hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ishaare se unhein apni jagah rehney ke liye kaha, is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne hath utha kar Allah ka shukr kya aur ultey paon peechhey aagey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aagey badh gaey."
1202,"ham pahley Namaz mein yun kaha kartey they falan par salam aur naam letey they. aur aapas mein aik shakhs doosrey ko salam kar letaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sun kar farmaya is tarah kaha karo. التحيات لله والصلوات والطيبات ، Mina Assalamualaik أيها النبي ورحمة الله وبركاته ، Mina السلام علينا وعلى عباد الله الصالحين ، Mina أشهد أن لا إله إلا الله وأشهد أن محمدا عبده ورسوله''yaanii saari Tahiyaat, bandagiyaan aur koshishein aur achi baatein khas Allah hi ke liye hain aur aey nabii! aap par salam ho, Allah ki rahmatein aur uski barkatein nazil hun. ham par salam ho aur Allah ke sab nek bandon par, main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur gawahi deta hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uske bandey aur rasool hain.'' agar tum ne ye padh liya to maano Allah ke un tamam Saleh bandon par salam pahuncha diya jo aasman aur zameen mein hain."
1203,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, (namaz mein agar koi baat pesh aa jaey to ( mardon ko Subhan-Allah kehna aur aurton ko hath par hath maarna chahiye (yani taali bajaa kar imam ko itlaa deni chahiye (note : taali seedhey hathon se nahi balke seedhey hath ko ultey hath par mar kar) ."
1204,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Subhan-Allah kehna mardon ke liye hai aur aurton ke liye taali bajaanaa."
1205,"peer ke roz musalman Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki iqtida (pairvi) mein fajr ki Namaz padh rahe they ke achcha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujrey ka parda hataaey huey dikhai diye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha ke sahaba saf baandhey khadey huey hain. ye dekh kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khul kar muskuraa diye Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ultey paon peechhey hatey . unhon-ne samjha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye tashrif laaengey aur musalman Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dekh kar us darja khush huey ke Namaz hi tod dalney ka irada kar liya. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hath ke ishara se hidayat ki ke Namaz poori karo. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne parda daal diya aur hujrey mein tashrif ley gaey. phir us din Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne intiqal farmaya,"
1206,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ( Bani-Israeel ki) aik aurat ne apne betey ko pukara , us waqt wo ibadat khaney mein tha. maan ne pukara ke aey Juraij ! Juraij ( to w pesh mein pad gaya aur dil mein) kehney laga ke aey Allah ! main ab maan ko dekhun ya Namaz ko . phir maan ne pukara : aey Juraij ! (wo ab bhi us to w pesh mein tha) ke aey Allah ! meri maan aur meri Namaz ! maan ne phir pukara : aey Juraij ! (wo ab bhi yahi ( sochey ja raha tha. aey Allah ! meri maan aur meri Namaz ! ( aakhir ( maan ne tang ho kar baddua ki aey Allah ! Juraij ko maut na aaey jab tak wo faahisha aurat ka chehra na dekh ley. Juraij ki ibadat gaah ke qareeb aik charaney wali aaya karti thi jo bakriyan charaatii thi. ittifaq se iske bachcha paida hua. logon ne puchha ke ye kis ka bachcha hai? usne kaha ke Juraij ka hai. wo aik martaba apni ibadat gaah se nikal kar mere paas raha tha. Juraij ne puchha ke wo aurat kon hai? jisne mujh par tohmat lagai hai ke iska bachcha mujh se hai. ( aurat bachchey ko lekar aai to ( unhon-ne bachchey se puchha ke bachchey ! tumhara bap kon ? bachcha bol padaa ke aik bakri charaney wala gadariya mera bap hai."
1207,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs se jo har martaba sajda kartey huey kankariyaan barabar karta tha farmaya agar aisa karna hai to sirf aik hi baar kar.
1208,ham sakht garmiyon mein jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhtey aur chehrey ko zameen par poori tarah rakhna mushkil ho jata to apna kapda bichhaa kar is par sajda kya kartey they.
1209,"mein apna paon Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney phaila leti thi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padhtey hotey jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sajda karne lagtey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey hath lagaatey , main paon samet leti , phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey ho jatey to main phaila leti ."
1210,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik martaba aik Namaz padhi phir farmaya ke mere samney aik shaitan aa gaya aur koshish karne laga ke meri Namaz tod de. lekin Allah Taala ne usko mere qaabu mein kar diya maine iska gala ghontaa ya usko dhakel diya. aakhir mein mera irada hua ke usey masjid ke aik sutoon se baandh dun aur jab subah ho to tum bhi dekho. lekin mujhey Sulaiman (Alaihissalam) ki dua yad aa gaee ''aey Allah ! mujhey aisi saltanat ata kiijiyo jo mere baad kisi aur ko na miley'' (is liye maine usey chhod diyaa) aur Allah Taala ne usey zillat ke sath bhagaa diya. iske baad Nazar-bin-Shumail ne kaha ke) ذعته ( ''zaal'' se hai. jiske mana hain ke maine iska gala ghont diya aur) دعته ( Allah Taala ke us qaul se liya gaya hai. ( يوم يدعون‏ ( jiske mana hain qiyamat ke din wo dozakh ki taraf dhakeley jaengey. durust pahlaa hi lafz hai. albatta Shoba ne isi tarah ''عین'' aur ''تاء'' ki tashdeed ke sath bayan kya hai.
1211,ham Ahwaaz mein (jo kai bastiyan hain Basra aur Iraan ke beech mein) khaarijiyon se jang kar rahe they. aik baar main nehar ke kinarey betha tha. itney mein aik shakhs ( abu-Barza sahabi (rz)) aaya aur Namaz padhney laga. kya dekhta hun ke unke ghodey ki lagaam unke hath mein hai. achcha ghoda unse chhoot kar bhaagney laga. to wo bhi uska peechhaa karne lagey. Shoba ne kaha ye abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) they. ye dekh kar khawaarij mein se aik shakhs kehney laga ke aey Allaah! us Shekh ka naas kar. jab wo Shekh wapas lautey to farmaya ke maine tumhari baatein sun li hain. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chh ya saat (7) ya aath (8) jihaadon mein shirkat ki hai aur maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aasaaniyon ko dekha hai. isliye mujhey ye achchha malum hua ke apna ghoda sath lekar lautoon na ke usko chhod dun wo jahan chahey chal de aur main takleef uthaaoon .
1212,"jab suraj girahan laga to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (namaz ke liye) khadey huey aur aik lambi sura padhi. phir rukoo kya aur bahut lamba rukoo kya. phir sar uthaya iske baad dusri sura shuru kar di, phir rukoo kya aur rukoo pura karke us rakaat ko khatm kya aur sajdey mein gaey. phir dusri rakaat mein bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isi tarah kya, Namaz se farigh ho kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke suraj aur chaand Allah ki nishaniyon mein se do nishaniyan hain. isliye jab tum unmein girahan dekho to Namaz shuru kar do jab tak ke ye saaf ho jaey aur dekho maine apni usi jagah se un tamam chizon ko dekh liya hai jinka mujh se wada hai. yahan tak ke maine ye bhi dekha ke main jannat ka aik khosha lena chahta hun. abhi tum logon ne dekha hoga ke main aagey badhney laga tha aur maine dozakh bhi dekhi (is haalat mein ke) kuchh aag kuchh aag ko khaaey ja rahi thi. tum logon ne dekha hoga ke jahannam ke us haulnaak manzar ko dekh kar mein peechhey hat gaya tha. maine jahannam ke andar Amr-bin-Luhyi ko dekha. ye wo shakhs hai jisne saand ki rasm Arab mein jari ki thi. (note : saand ki rasm se murad ke ontni ko ghairullaah ke naam par chhod dena yahan tak ke sawari aur doodh bhi na dhonaa.)"
1213,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik baar masjid mein qible ki taraf raint dekhi . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein maujood logon par bahut naraz huey aur farmaya ke Allah Taala tumharey samney hai isliye Namaz mein thooka na karo, ya ye farmaya ke raint na nikala karo. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) utrey aur khud hi apne hath se usey khurch dala. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jab kisi ko thookna zaroori ho to apni baain taraf thook ley."
1214,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum mein se koi Namaz mein ho to wo apne rab se sargoshi karta hai, isliye usko samney na thookna chahiye aur na daain taraf albatta baain taraf apne qadam ke nichey thook ley."
1215,log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz is tarah padhtey ke tehband chhotey honey ki wjah se unhein apni gardanon se baandhey rakhtey aur aurton ko (jo mardon ke peechhey jamat mein Sharik rehti thiin) keh diya jata ke jab tak mard poori tarah simat kar na baith jayen tum apne sar (sajdey se) na uthaanaa.
1216,( shuruaat Islam mein) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Namaz mein hotey to main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam karta to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jawab detey they. magar jab ham ( Habsha se jahan hijrat ki thi) wapas aaey to maine (pahley ki tarah Namaz mein) salam kya. magar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi jawab nahi diya (kyonke ab Namaz mein baat cheet wghaira ki manaahii nazil ho gaee thi) aur farmaya ke Namaz mein us se mashghooliyat hoti hai.
1217,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey apni aik zarurat ke liye (ghuzwa bani mustaliq mein) bhejaa. mein wapas aaya aur maine kaam pura kar diya tha. phir maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi jawab nahi diya. mere dil mein Allah janey kya baat aai aur maine apne dil mein kaha ke shayad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujh par isliye khafa hain ke main der se aaya hun. maine phir dobara salam kya aur jab us martaba bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne koi jawab na diya to ab mere dil mein pahley se bhi zyada khayal aaya. phir maine ( teesri martaba ( salam kya, aur ab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab diya aur farmaya ke pahley jo 2 baar maine jawab na diya to us wjah se tha ke main Namaz padh raha tha, aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt apni ontni par they aur iska rukh qible ki taraf na tha balke dusri taraf tha."
1218,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye khabar pahunchi ke Quba ke qabila banu-Amr-bin-Auf mein koi jhagdaa ho gaya hai. isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kai ashaab ko sath lekar unmein suleh karaaney ke liye tashrif ley gaey. wahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) suleh safaaii ke liye thahar gaey. idhar Namaz ka waqt ho gaya to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nahi aaey aur Namaz ka waqt ho gaya, to kya aap logon ko Namaz padhaaeingey ? aap ne jawab diya ke haan agar tum chahtey ho to padha doonga . chunanche Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne takbeer kahi aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aagey badh kar niyat baandh li. itney main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi tashrif ley aaey aur safon se guzartey huey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pehli saf mein aa khadey huey, logon ne hath par hath maarney shuru kar diye. ( Sehal ne kaha ke) تصفيح (ke mana ( تصفيق (ke hain) aap ne bayan kya ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz mein kisi taraf mutwajjeh nahi hotey they. lekin jab logon ne bahut dastakein diin to unhon-ne dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ishara se Abu-Bakar ko Namaz padhaaney ke liye kaha, is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne hath utha kar Allah Taala ka shukr ada kya aur phir ultey paon peechhey ki taraf chaley aaey aur saf mein khadey ho gaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aagey badh kar Namaz padhai. Namaz se farigh ho kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya ke logo ! ye kya baat hai ke jab Namaz mein koi baat pesh aati hai to tum taaliyaan bajaaney lagtey ho. ye masla to aurton ke liye hai. tumhen agar Namaz mein koi haadisa pesh aaey to ( sub'haanallaah) kaha karo. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya ke Abu-Bakar ! mere kehney ke bawajud tum ne Namaz kyon nahi padhai ? Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke abu-Qahaafa ke betey ko zeb nahi deta ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki maujoodgii mein Namaz padhaaey ."
1219,"Namaz mein pahlu par hath rakhney se mana kya gaya tha. Hisham aur abu-Hilaal Muhammad-bin Saleem ne, Ibne-Sirin se us hadis ko riwayat kya, wo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
1220,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pahlu par hath rakh kar Namaz padhney se mana farmaya,"
1221,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Asr ki Namaz padhi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) salam phertey hi badi tezi se uthey aur apni aik biwi ke hujre mein tashrif le gaey, phir bahar tashrif laey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni jaldi par us tajjub w hairat ko mehsus kya jo sahaba ke chehron se zahir ho raha tha, isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Namaz mein mujhey soney ka aik daala yad aa gaya jo hamarey paas taqseem se baqi reh gaya tha. mujhey bura malum hua ke hamarey paas wo Sham (Syria) tak ya raat tak reh jaey. isliye maine usey taqseem karne ka hukm de diya."
1222,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab Namaz ke liye azan di jati hai to shaitan peeth mod kar hawa khaarij karta hua bhaagta hai taake azan na sun sakey. jab muazzan chup ho jata hai to mardood phir aa jata hai aur jab jamat khadi honey lagti hai (aur takbeer kahi jati hai) to phir bhag jata hai. lekin jab muazzan chup ho jata hai to phir aa jata hai. aur aadmi ke dil mein waswasey paida karta rehta hai. kehta hai ke) falan-falan baat ( yad kar. kambakht wo baatein yad dilata hai jo us namazi ke zahan mein bhi na thin. is tarah namazi ko ye bhi yad nahi rehta ke usne kitni rakatein padhi hain. abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne kaha ke jab koi ye bhool jaey (ke kitni rakatein padhi hain) to baithey baithey ( saho ke) 2 sajdey kar ley. abu-Salma ne ye Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna tha.
1223,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha log kehtey hain ke Abu-Hurera bahut zyada hadisein bayan karta hai (aur haal ye hai ke) mein aik shakhs se aik martaba mila aur us se maine ( bataur imtihaan ( malum kya ke pichhli raat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne isha mein kon kaun si soortein padhi thin ? usne kaha ke mujhey nahi malum . maine puchha ke tum Namaz mein Sharik they? kaha ke haan, Sharik tha. maine kaha lekin mujhey to yad hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne falan-falan soortein padhi thin."
